@startuml
title Withdraw Member with Auth API

actor User
participant MemberController
participant MemberCommandService
participant MemberCommandRepository
entity Member
participant DomainEventPublisher #skyblue
participant AuthController

User -> MemberController : DELETE /users/me
MemberController -> MemberCommandService : withdrawMemberById(memberId)

MemberCommandService -> MemberCommandRepository : findById(memberId)
MemberCommandRepository --> MemberCommandService : Member

' 인증 세션 무효화를 위해 AuthController에 요청
MemberCommandService -> AuthController : DELETE /internal/auth/members/{memberId}

alt 인증 삭제 성공
AuthController --> MemberCommandService : HTTP 200 OK
MemberCommandService -> Member : withdraw()
MemberCommandService -> MemberCommandRepository : save(member)
MemberCommandService -> DomainEventPublisher : publish(memberWithdrawEvent)
MemberCommandService --> MemberController : 탈퇴 성공

MemberController --> User : HTTP 204 No Content
User -> User : redirect(main page)

else 인증 삭제 실패
AuthController --> MemberCommandService : HTTP 500 Error
MemberCommandService --> MemberController : 탈퇴 중단
MemberController --> User : HTTP 500 Internal Server Error

end
@enduml